com.diffplug.common.rx

Class GuardedExecutor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.diffplug.common.rx.GuardedExecutor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RxSubscriber, Executor

    public class GuardedExecutor
extends Object
implements Executor, RxSubscriber
    GuardedExecutor is an Executor and RxSubscriber which promises to cancel its subscriptions and stop executing tasks once its getGuard() has been disposed. Useful for tying asynchronous tasks to gui elements.
